@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";

}
<head>
    <style>

        /* CSS is defined here for simplicity. Move this to a .css file! */
        :root {
            --royal-blue: #002D62; /* Deep, professional blue */
            --gold-accent: #FFD700; /* Pure gold */
            --light-bg: #F0F8FF; /* Off-white / light blue */
            --text-color: #333;
        }

        .about-page-container {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--light-bg);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            color: var(--text-color);
        }

        .about-section-header {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: var(--royal-blue);
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--gold-accent);
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .about-text-block {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        .highlight-box {
            background-color: #E6E6FA; /* A subtle lavender/periwinkle */
            border-left: 5px solid var(--gold-accent);
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

            .highlight-box h3 {
                color: var(--royal-blue);
                margin-top: 0;
                font-weight: 600;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<div class="about-page-container">
    <h1 class="about-section-header">About Us: Stay Ease – Your Smart Accommodation Partner</h1>
    <div class="about-text-block">
        <p>Stay Ease is a technology-based platform dedicated to modernizing the paying guest (PG) accommodation experience. We simplify the search, booking, and management of various PG types—including Girls PG's, Boys PG's, and Co-Living PG's—through smart filtering by location, price, room type, amenities, and more.</p>
        <p>Launched to provide a secure and seamless digital solution, we are committed to expanding our service across major cities to support tenants and administrators nationwide.</p>
    </div>
    <h2 class="about-section-header" style="font-size: 2em;">What are we aiming at?</h2>
    <div class="about-text-block">
        <p>Our primary aim is to deliver a secure, transparent, and user-friendly digital ecosystem for PG accommodation.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>**For Tenants (Guests):** To provide a robust search engine that accurately matches users with their ideal PG based on specific needs (type, duration, budget), enabling secure online booking and payment.</li>
            <li>**For Administrators (Homeowners):** To offer powerful management tools for handling listings, tracking room availability, managing food menus, processing rent payments, and efficiently addressing tenant feedback.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <h2 class="about-section-header" style="font-size: 2em;">Who we are?</h2>
    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h3>A Foundation of Trust and Technology</h3>
        <p>We are the next generation of accommodation management. Stay Ease is built on a foundation of reliability and smart technology (ASP.NET, C#, and SQL Server).</p>
        <ul>
            <li>We are a team focused on providing a **personalized and inclusive experience** by clearly categorizing PG options (Girls, Boys, Co-Living).</li>
            <li>We ensure the safety and satisfaction of all parties through secure payment gateways, clear communication channels (notifications, suggestion box), and a well-defined admin structure.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>